@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant Gateway
participant VMService
participant Worker
participant OpenNebula

User -> Frontend: Create VM
Frontend -> Gateway: POST /vms
Gateway -> VMService: Create request
VMService -> Worker: enqueue provisioning
Worker -> OpenNebula: create VM from template
OpenNebula --> Worker: VM ID + status
Worker --> VMService: update status
VMService --> Gateway: response
Gateway --> Frontend: VM created
@enduml
